# Development Script to Activate User for Testing

This script allows you to bypass email verification in development by directly activating a user account using the Supabase admin API.

## Usage

```bash
node scripts/dev-activate-user.js <email>
```

## Example

```bash
node scripts/dev-activate-user.js test_operator_007@gmail.com
```

## Requirements

- Supabase credentials must be configured in `.env.local`
- Requires `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` for admin access

## Notes

- This script should only be used in development
- Never use this in production as it bypasses security measures